added.title: Caillou Tries Karate/Just Like Daddy/Caillou's Safari/Cowboy Caillou
added.description: Leo comes over to play at Caillou's house./Daddy has a list of things to do around the house./Caillou wants to play with his animal cards but they have disappeared./Jonas, a friend of Dad's and a real cowboy, has invited the family to visit his ranch.

added.title: Caillou Goes Shopping/Caillou Goes Apple Picking/Caillou's Halloween Costume
added.description: Caillou's crayons are all worn down or broken, so Mommy suggests a trip to the store for some new ones./Caillou's playschool is on a special field trip to an apple orchard./Halloween is coming and it's time to pick out a costume to wear.

added.title: Coins/Canoe Trip/The Bulldozer/The Firefighter/The Timekeeper
added.description: Caillou accompanies Mom to the grocery store./When Caillou, Grandpa and Daddy go on a canoe trip, Caillou gets to see some wild animals./On an autumn day, Caillou and his Mommy take a walk and pass by a construction site./When Dad's burning toasts trigger the fire alarm, he decides it is the perfect opportunity to practice a fire drill./Caillou and his Mommy are finishing preparing a picnic lunch.

added.title: Elephants!/Caillou and the Sheep/Caillou and the Puppies/The Duck Family/Clementine's New Pet
added.description: When Mom, Rosie and Caillou go to the zoo, Caillou can't wait to see the elephants./Grandma takes Caillou on a special visit to a sheep farm./Caillou and Dad go over to Mr. Hinkle's house to help him build a dog house./While Caillou and his family are on a picnic at the park, his beach ball accidentally rolls into a pond./When Mom takes Caillou to Clementine's to see her new pet, she won't tell Caillou what kind of animal it is.

added.title: Disappearing Carrots/Caillou Marches On/Who's Mooing/Follow That Sound!/The Music Box!
added.description: When a white rabbit eats a bunch of carrots set aside for a picnic lunch, Caillou and Rosie go looking him./When Caillou visits Clementine, he is impressed to see Billy practicing on a tuba./Caillou and his family are leaving for a picnic in the country but the ride feels very long for Caillou./On a winter evening, a strange sound grabs Caillou's attention./Caillou goes up to the attic with Mom and finds a box containing a teddy bear and a music box.

added.title: Three Cheers for Cheer
added.description: When hard-working Cheer exhausts her crew running a string of drills to protect a Whiffle orchard from possible emergencies, Share's belly badge accidentally creates two Cheer duplicates. Cheer takes a recreation break, unaware that her clones are working Share and the crew - who think they're the real Cheer - even harder.

added.title: The Badge of Courage
added.description: When Dibble dresses up as a superhero complete with a pretend belly badge, the Whiffles think she's the real thing and need her to confront an imaginary monster that they believe lives in a cave. She bravely enters the cave but loses her courage when she loses the belly badge, until Funshine convinces her that her bravery came from inside her.

added.title: Boot Castle/Avocado's Long Time Out/Tanks Giving
added.description: Findley discovers a boot that him and Lucas use as a castle./ When they hear Avocado has been put in her naughty crate, Lucas and Findley entertain her./ Lucas brings Dimples things from around the house so she doesn't feel left out.

added.title: Flying/Dr. Lucas is in the House/Arlo's Portrait
added.description: After watching Findley in flight, Lucas wonders what it would be like to fly./ Dr. Lucas tries to make all his friends feel better but ends up under the weather himself./ Lucas decides to paint a portrait of Arlo. But Arlo can't sit still.

added.title: Flush Hour
added.description: The babies learn the purpose of toilets.

added.title: I Strain
added.description: Petunia gets hooked on watching television and stops playing with her friends.

added.title: Let's Go Camping!
added.description: A camping trip is planned - but Pocoyo and Pato have too much luggage. In the end they realize that all you really need for a nice camping trip are your friends - and then it doesn't really matter whether you're at home or away.

added.title: Pocoyo, Pocoyo
added.description: Pocoyo discovers a fabulous new playmate - his echoooo-ooo-ooo-ooo!

added.title: Elly's Big Chase
added.description: Elly inadvertently sets off on a fantastic journey - all the while fast asleep on her chair - as Pocoyo and Pato protect her from danger.

added.title: Pocoyo Gets it Right
added.description: Pocoyo wants to play 'pitch and putt' like his friends, Pocoyo and Elly, but he can't quite get the hang of it. He watches carefully and finally grasps where he was going wrong.

added.title: Juggling Balls
added.description: Pocoyo is very impressed with Elly and Octopus' trick of juggling. He wants to play too. Octopus makes Pocoyo practice lots of different activities but Pocoyo can't see the point because they aren't related to juggling… or so he thinks. In the end Pocoyo becomes the star of the show!

removed.description: Today Pocoyo is Super Pocoyo - a superhero determined to rescue his friends from tight fixes - even when they don't need to be rescued.
